&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; &quot;underlying unity&quot; is to create another kind of polarity.  The
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; teachings of nonduality are still about disengatement and detachment,
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; &quot;release from the all&quot; or any concept of &quot;all.&quot;

